twitch_info.title: I Wanna AA BlackY Mix clear
twitch_info.description:
My most recent rare venture into avoidance, which I enjoyed. It looks really chaotic, but a lot of that is actually pattern which were kinda arduous parts for me to learn, but satisfying to get past. The rest is ez rng, except one part that took me a while to get the hang of.
Thanks to desti!
